location.fullValue: Daniel Plan, Oak Ridge at Crystal Valley

data.description: Welcome to this gorgeous 3-bed, 3-bath home, a true gem nestled on a scenic corner lot! Displaying a 3-car garage and stone accents details that elevate the external charm. Come inside to find an open floor plan that effortlessly blends functionality with style, offering a spacious and versatile area that caters to a modern lifestyle! The interior shows elegance with neutral paint, recessed lighting, and a mix of plush carpeting & chic wood-look flooring, perfectly balancing comfort and style. The heart of this home is undoubtedly the kitchen! Sleek SS appliances, granite counters, a walk-in pantry, ample white cabinetry, and a prep island with a breakfast bar complete the picture. Retreat to the main bedroom, featuring an ensuite with dual granite sinks and a large walk-in closet. Want MORE? The finished basement is the highlight of this abode! It provides a flexible and expansive area suitable for various activities, from a cozy family entertainment zone to a personal gym or hobby space, all within the inviting ambiance of your own home. Discover the backyard, where an open patio awaits! It serves as an ideal setting for outdoor get-togethers, peaceful morning coffees, or simply basking in the serene beauty of your surroundings. Located in the desirable Crystal Valley Ranch, this home is part of a Community boasting an outdoor pool, fitness center, playing fields, a dog park, and miles of walking & biking paths for an active lifestyle. Enjoy close proximity to shopping, restaurants, and I-25! Don't miss this fantastic opportunity!
